acid arrow
Level-2nd
CastingTime-1Action
Range/Area-90ft
School-Evocation
Attack/Save-Ranged
Damage-4d4
OtherInfo-                A shimmering green arrow streaks toward a target within range and bursts in a sray of acid. Make a ranged sell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes 4d4 acid damage immediately and 2d4 acid damage at the end of its next turn. On a miss, the arrow slashes the target with acid for half as much of the initial damage and no damage at the end of its next turn.
